tweet_raw: CRYPTO PAYMENTS UPDATEOver the past weekend our current Crypto Payment Processor Coinbase implemented several changes to their payment gateway. We have become aware that these adjustments have resulted in some customers being unable to complete their purchases using Cryptocurrency.In response to this situation we entered into an agreement with a new Crypto Payment Processor Confirmo yesterday. Confirmo enables the seamless sending of Cryptocurrency to a wallet address just as it was before. Additionally Confirmo supports transactions over alternative networks including the Tron Network (TRX).Our In-House Development Team is currently working on integrating Confirmo into our system. We anticipate completing this integration within the week thereby making Crypto Payments at BrightFunded smoother and more user-friendly than ever.
